## Key Features

- Vision-first with automatic intelligent fallback
- Built-in PII redaction (email & phone)
- Retry logic with exponential backoff
- Full argparse CLI + JSON output + silent mode
- Recursive folder support
- Enhanced image metadata description in fallback mode
- Session tracking, latency metrics, and heartbeat (every 5.55 minutes)

